      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp ZF 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the Double VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and rod bearings have been addressed for preventative longevity. The chassis is structurally perfect with zero subframe fatigue, supported by a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the paint retains its factory depth with no swirl marks. A truly analog driving experience with a documented service history, this M-car represents the peak of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated engineering.",
