      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, and it shows. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, thanks to a professional ceramic coating applied annually. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather upholstery still carries that distinct factory aroma, with absolutely zero bolster wear or creasing. Every switch, dial, and electronic component functions with the crisp precision of a new car. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive binder of service records from day one. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full fluid flush and a new set of high-performance tires. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
